eurocars: Annual Sales of Cars in Europe

Source: R/data-eurocars.R
eurocars.Rd

Annual model-level sales of cars in European countries between 1970 and 1999.

data('eurocars')

Format

A data.frame with 11,549 observations on 39 variables:
